  "license_key_placeholder": "bijv. TEST-20260126-001",
  "license_online_licensing": "Online licentieverlening",
  "license_online_info_html": "<b>Online licentieverlening met Supabase</b>\n\n    • <b>GRATIS licentie:</b> gratis activering op basis van e-mail\n    • <b>GRATIS quotum:</b> eenmalig 250 afbeeldingen (levenslang)\n    • <b>PRO-licentie:</b> onbeperkte afbeeldingen + premiumfuncties\n    • <b>Cloud Sync:</b> Licentiestatus wordt gesynchroniseerd nadat de verbinding is hersteld\n\n<b>Plannen:</b>\n    • <b>FREE</b> - Starter (in totaal 250 afbeeldingen)\n    • <b>PRO</b> - Professioneel (Cloud, 3 apparaten, onbeperkt)\n\n<b>Activering:</b>\nVoer hierboven uw licentiesleutel in en klik op \"Activeren\".\n    Het apparaat wordt automatisch geregistreerd.",
  "license_plan_comparison_html": "<style>\n    tabel { border-collapse: collapse; width: 100%; margin: 10px 0; }\n    e { background: #333; color: white; padding: 12px; text-align: center; font-weight: bold; }\n    td { padding: 10px; border: 1px solid #444; text-align: center; }\n    .featurenaam { text-align: left; font-weight: bold; background: #2a2a2a; }\n    .check { color: #4CAF50; font-size: 18px; }\n    .cross { color: #666; font-size: 18px; }\n    .abonnementsvrij { background: #1a1a1a; }\n    .plan-pro { background: #2a2a2a; }\n    .prijs { font-size: 20px; font-weight: bold; color: #FF9800; }\n    .highlight { background: #FF9800; color: white; padding: 4px 8px; border-radius: 4px; }\n</style>\n\n<h2>Planvergelijking</h2>\n\n<table>\n    <tr>\n        <th class=\"feature-name\">Functie / Limiet</th>\n        <th class=\"plan-free\">GRATIS<br><span class=\"price\">€0</span></th>\n        <th class=\"plan-pro\">PRO<br><span class=\"price\">vanaf € 19/jaar</span></th>\n    </tr>\n    \n    <!-- Basic Features -->\n    <tr>\n        <td class=\"feature-name\">Beeldanalyse en dubbeldetectie</td>\n        <td class=\"plan-free\">Ja</td>\n        <td class=\"plan-pro\">Ja</td>\n    </tr>\n    <tr>\n        <td class=\"feature-name\">Afbeeldingslimiet</td>\n        <td class=\"plan-free\">250 afbeeldingen totaal</td>\n        <td class=\"plan-pro\"><span class=\"highlight\">Onbeperkt</span></td>\n    </tr>\n    <tr>\n        <td class=\"feature-name\">Apparaatlimiet</td>\n        <td class=\"plan-free\">1 apparaat</td>\n        <td class=\"plan-pro\">3 apparaten</td>\n    </tr>\n    \n    <!-- PRO Features -->\n    <tr>\n        <td class=\"feature-name\">Batchverwerking (massa-import)</td>\n        <td class=\"plan-free\">Nee</td>\n        <td class=\"plan-pro\">Ja</td>\n    </tr>\n    <tr>\n        Ondersteuning voor <td class=\"feature-name\">HEIC/HEIF-indeling</td>\n        <td class=\"plan-free\">Nee</td>\n        <td class=\"plan-pro\">Ja</td>\n    </tr>\n    <tr>\n        <td class=\"feature-name\">Uitgebreide caching (2-8x sneller)</td>\n        <td class=\"plan-free\">Nee</td>\n        <td class=\"plan-pro\">Ja</td>\n    </tr>\n    <tr>\n        <td class=\"feature-name\">Kwaliteitsanalyse (scherpte/belichting/details)</td>\n        <td class=\"plan-free\">Basis</td>\n        <td class=\"plan-pro\"><span class=\"highlight\">Geavanceerd</span></td>\n    </tr>\n    <tr>\n        <td class=\"feature-name\">Batchverwijdering</td>\n        <td class=\"plan-free\">Nee</td>\n        <td class=\"plan-pro\">Ja</td>\n    </tr>\n    <tr>\n        <td class=\"feature-name\">Exportformaten (CSV, JSON)</td>\n        <td class=\"plan-free\">Nee</td>\n        <td class=\"plan-pro\">Ja</td>\n    </tr>\n    <tr>\n        <td class=\"feature-name\">Ondersteuning</td>\n        <td class=\"plan-free\">Nee</td>\n        <td class=\"plan-pro\">E-mail</td>\n    </tr>\n    <tr>\n        <td class=\"feature-name\">Offline respijtperiode</td>\n        <td class=\"plan-free\">-</td>\n        <td class=\"plan-pro\">7 dagen</td>\n    </tr>\n</table>\n\n<br>\n<p><b>💡 Aanbeveling:</b></p>\n<ul>\n    <li><b>GRATIS:</b> Testen en kleine verzamelingen (tot 250 afbeeldingen in totaal)</li>\n    <li><b>PRO:</b> Regelmatig gebruik met onbeperkte afbeeldingen</li>\n</ul>",
